Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.52,0:27:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have it?\N>> Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.72,0:27:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, sometimes I struggle with um trying\Nto find the difference between going
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.60,0:27:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,through an experience and juicing it.\NSo, I was wondering if you could
