Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.24,0:27:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,utilizing it for some secondary gain.\NThere's a secondary gain. So to
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.55,0:27:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,relinquish it, all you have to do is\Nspot what is the secondary gain and be
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.36,0:27:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,willing to surrender the secondary gain.\NDon't forget in return for surrendering
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.84,0:28:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the secondary gain of that which is\Nnegative. In return, you get the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.32,0:28:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,positive gain of that which is positive.\N>> Mhm. So you feel better about yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.44,0:28:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,when you've forgiven somebody even\Nthough they did actually, you know, did
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.03,0:28:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,do you something wrong\Nuh than you do by harboring the
