Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.20,0:28:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,up because it thinks I'm giving up all\Nthis wonderful juice of hate and
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.15,0:28:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,resentment and feeling sorry for myself\Nuh in return for nothing. No, you get
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.60,0:28:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,something back. And after you do it a\Nfew times and find that you feel much
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.96,0:28:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,better about yourself than you did\Nbefore you let it go, it then becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.27,0:28:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,easier each time.\N>> Mhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.44,0:28:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Every time you let a resentment go, you\Nfeel better than you did
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.79,0:28:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,when you were having the resentment.\NSee, for one thing, you don't have the
