Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.08,0:30:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more like out of this arises the\Nwhole
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.39,0:30:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,panorama of all that is possible. And\Nnow as you as a spiritual reality have
