Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.27,0:31:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Okay. Thank you very much.\NSo just
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.60,0:31:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,>> wish to express my heartfelt gratitude\Nfor all that is in the field at this
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.88,0:31:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,moment and all that have contributed to\Nthis possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.79,0:31:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been a student of yours since the\Nbeginning of 03.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.27,0:31:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Had the opportunity now to be in your\Npresence three times
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.51,0:31:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and every time I've been before you\Nbefore or in your presence that uh the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.27,0:31:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,answers to the questions I've developed\Nhave all formulated and I've not had the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.00,0:32:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,opportunity to come up or the reason to\Ncome up and see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.91,0:32:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The question I pose is coming from a\Nspace of of non-duality and totally
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.76,0:32:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,non-positionality,\Nhow does one make a stand for truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.20,0:32:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Actually, it's a whole lecture in\Nitself. But without positionality, you
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.84,0:32:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,merely stand being what you are. See,\Nthe eagle stands being an eagle. Not in
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.08,0:32:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,order to scare doves, not in order to\Nnot for any reason at all. It just is an
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.96,0:32:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,eagle because that's fulfilling its\Neagle nature. You see? So when you stand
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.72,0:32:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,for truth, it's not like you're standing\Nin opposition to falsehood. You're
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.36,0:32:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,really standing for truth. You see?\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.48,0:33:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Uh so it it is a strength. It is a\Nstrength to stand for uh the truth as
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.24,0:33:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you understand it.\NTo do so by being it,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.84,0:33:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,not to please anyone or to accomplish.\NIn other words, no, there's no purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.76,0:33:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to it.\NIt's just because that's the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.79,0:33:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So I have a certain obligation as a\Nteacher. I f is my understanding of it
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.08,0:33:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to fulfill that to fulfill that to have\Nthe strength to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.44,0:33:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for any particular reason except to\Nfulfill one's potential which is all
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.55,0:33:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that God really gives us is potential.\NAnd and my understanding would be
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.20,0:33:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,an appreciation for the gift of the\Npotential to fulfill it to the best of
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.88,0:33:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,your capacity and thus to serve God.\NThat might be by being the best athlete,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.44,0:34:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the best cab driver, a good husband,\Ngood father, forgiving citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.00,0:34:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows what it means? Because at each\Nlevel it means something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.48,0:34:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming.\N>> Hello, Dr. Hawkins. How do we what can
