Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.56,0:34:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,since we see them seldom?\N>> Do you see them very often?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.00,0:34:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,a couple times a year.\N>> Well, you attract them. You try to
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.96,0:34:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,attract them into things you you think\Nwould be contributo to that direction.
