Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.92,0:35:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you when they passed out?" Be\Nprepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.83,0:36:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So you encourage them into things that\Nuh that will carry them in the direction
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.28,0:36:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,you want them to go. Yeah.\N>> Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.83,0:36:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Appreciation for beauty and all such\Nthings.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.07,0:36:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thank you.\N>> Yeah.
