Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.68,0:42:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,of infinite glory beyond all description\Nforever more.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.20,0:43:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It only has to be gone through once,\Nbut it's never been gone through before.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.04,0:43:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can die hundreds of times and never\Ngo through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.96,0:43:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But it came up, so I did it.\NAlso, it brought up the fear of
