Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.31,0:44:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in comparison to an infinite\Neverythingness of God as absolute bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.00,0:44:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore realizing the mistake I\Nbacked out of it because the presence of
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.31,0:44:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,God is signified by a profound and\Ninfinite love. Profound. Staggeringly.
